OL,3,CThree charged with murder of man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FThree people have been charged with
OL,7,Fthe murder of a man who was stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath in Market Rasen.
OL,10,F37-year-old Danny Fowler was found
OL,11,Fwith several wounds on Union Street on
OL,12,Fthe evening of Thursday 12 March and
OL,13,Fdied later in hospital.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, Lincolnshire Police
OL,16,Fconfirmed they have charged Ryan
OL,17,FTownhill, 29, of no fixed address,
OL,18,FMartin Doocey, 55, of Waverley Court,
OL,19,FQueen Street, Market Rasen and Shannon
OL,20,FDoocey, 31, of Mill Street, Market
OL,21,FRasen with murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
