OL,3,CThree charged with murder of man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death
OL,6,FShannon Doocey has also been charged
OL,7,Fwith having an offensive weapon in a
OL,8,Fpublic place and Ryan Townhill has
OL,9,Fbeen charged with having a bladed
OL,10,Farticle in a public place.
OL,12,FJoshua Wood, 23, of Malvern Road,
OL,13,FScunthorpe, has been charged with
OL,14,Fthreatening with an offensive weapon
OL,15,Fin a public place.
OL,17,FAll four have been remanded into
OL,18,Fcustody and will appear before Lincoln
OL,19,FMaigstrates' Court on Monday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
